The [east-west 7-stone band at $2,510](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/east-west-7-stone-emerald-diamond-anniversary-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-5-8-ct-tw-item-150312?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is a different interpretation. The stones sit in a horizontal orientation, which pairs perfectly with a traditional solitaire where the center stone sits in a standard north-south orientation. The contrast is deliberate.

