The [$1,255 hidden halo](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-hidden-halo-solitaire-plus-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-item-192506?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the best compromise for buyers who love the idea of a halo but don't want to ruin the outline. Look at the ring from above: clean rectangle. Look at it from the side: a rim of diamonds. It's a deliberate design choice, not a compromise.

