## Final Verdict: Best Emerald Cut Diamond Ring Setting for You

**Best for minimal spend**: [$690 Petite Solitaire in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/rings/petite-emerald-cut-solitaire-diamond-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-311196?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Four prongs, narrow band, no extras. The stone owns the entire look.

**Best for active lifestyle**: [$990 Comfort Fit Bezel Solitaire in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/comfort-fit-bezel-set-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315709?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Full corner coverage, no snagging, comfortable inner edge for daily wear.

**Best for presence without a halo**: [$2,090 Common Prong Pavé in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/common-prong-diamond-pave-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-310923?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). A full pavé band adds sparkle that runs alongside the stone, not around it.

**Best for a distinctive look**: [$2,720 Bezel Baguette Three-Stone in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-straight-baguette-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-316318?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Three step-cut stones on one ring, the baguettes framing and echoing the center stone.

